  "37:5": ["[رَّبُّ] al-Samāwāt and Al-Arḍ and Not/what Between them two [وَرَبُّ] [ٱلْمَشَٰرِقِ]",""],
  "37:6": ["Indeed We [زَيَّنَّا] al-Samāʾ al-Dunyā [بِزِينَةٍ] al-Kawākib",""],
